# Loomis — Mobile Delivery

## Mobile-native layout archetypes (pick one — do not invent per screen)

| Archetype | Routes |
|---|---|
| **HomeHub** | Parent/student/teacher home |
| **ChildContextHub** | Parent per-child views |
| **TimelineList** | Attendance history |
| **SummaryDetail** | Results, fees |
| **DaySchedule** | Timetable |
| **SubmissionFlow** | Assignments |
| **SettingsForm** | Contact/settings |
| **AuthShell** | Login/MFA/reset |
| **QuickMarkGrid** | Class teacher attendance |
| **GradeEntrySheet** | Teacher score entry |
| **OfflineBanner** | Global pending sync |

Reference: `apps/mobile/src/app/(dev)/showcase.tsx` in `__DEV__`.

## Forbidden (causes rework)

- Porting web `PageHeader`, sidebar, or overlapping KPI hero cards
- Stock Expo tab styling with no brand tokens
- Outline-only primary CTAs
- ScrollView for long lists (use FlashList)
- Arbitrary hex colors — use `@loomis/design-tokens` / `MOBILE_THEME`
- Inline one-off styled controls in `apps/mobile` — extend `@loomis/ui-mobile` first

## Required

- Touch targets ≥ 44pt
- Loading skeleton matches final layout shape
- Light + dark mode
- `can(role, capability)` for UI gating
- Money via `formatKobo` / `CurrencyText`
- Offline writes → SQLite queue first, then sync engine
- Notification bodies: opaque deep-link IDs only (no PII/grades)

## Role stacks

- `(parent)`, `(student)` — online-first MVP
- `(class-teacher)`, `(teacher)` — offline queue for attendance/grade drafts
- School admin / platform — web only → `(auth)/unsupported`
